- timer 99","Brook Wingman Converters will be provided rather than requiring players bring their own. Converters are put in force digital mode (LED on the new model converter should be blue). This is more strictly enforced if a persons controller is capable of an uncleaned socd whether pure dpad or dpad + analog stick.
