KRSCH (Dolphin),recsj0Bo7neCk0Zti,48,70/20/10,https://matcherino.com/tournaments/132276,,rec6VT2mOKYXDd4VG,KRSCH,Double Elimination,2/3,2/3,Winner must keep character. Loser may switch.,"The Finisher Mode Throw Cancel bug is banned.

Tag Battle Style is banned (except when used to choose Fourze Meteor Fusion States).

Combo follow-ups after attacks that disable the opponent's burst are banned.
    This affects Kabuto, Den-O (PWR), Fourze Meteor Fusion States, and Kiva (off-axis Kiva Rider Art must be immediately followed up with 5S).
    This does not affect Kuuga (PWR) or Imperer, as their respective cinematics (Kuuga (PWR)'s Rider Art and Imperer's Rider Finale) do not disable burst.

Zeronos may not transform between Vega Form and Zero Form and vice-versa.
    If Zeronos transforms from Vega to Zero or vice-versa, then the player must immediately transform back to Altair Form.","3/5 Games for Losers Finals, 3/5 Games for Winners Finals, 3/5 Games for Grand Finals",https://v5.airtableusercontent.com/v3/u/41/41/1748088000000/lUtK4PjZXWUcVMlvD2iukA/vlfBvd2puRmRQ6krQ5PD1IzWlwsQN5-TjNHbjZKXLbk4ZVBmO1p9NG1kV9h2ewBx5FGxgZCBlZ6BNTutCFwlb6XAAsp0IbfILy_NK5u4GgFignGZGhF-jELDmgk1O9jAvUL33w8RQoV7gmZgxQZeX74xbxlua5y9yIl6-IiBrjU/PIyBcuX6Ot4Uu913rD3PfP5GNQWk0_UDBT66axauwjs,Kamen Rider Super Climax Heroes ,"Combo,Snivy",BunniesFromHell,KRSCH%20%28Dolphin%29,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a5n6fA96Q5s,72.5,Thurs. 1/23,1/23 Thu,https://www.start.gg/tournament/vortex-gallery-at-frosty-faustings-xvii/event/kamen-rider-super-climax-heroes/overview,2024-09-24T04:00:25.000Z,2,Kamen Rider,True,11,3 Hours,23%,11 / 48,,2,"rec2alQdZPRwPoDw0, recMLwp2z0aq4mUWl",KRSCH,"recIycapjtUKXX9yo, recWvs1VcnoxWYgBy, recWrUqjR1PClOzjG, rec7QBqvsAtPkTUXf, recCYSGVyfwsZGY5x, recKc3FbzKjXI4A8D, recoyq7aqw0hd3EEi, recXYQkwYso6cvtb4",2nd Lineup,recrOeOV5ZtWIGqXL,2025-02-07T15:41:16.000Z,https://www.twitch.tv/videos/2361824565,recGBJgB9TCcM7mDd,"Sat. 1/25, Sun. 1/26, Fri. 1/24","rechpVTO125agNeFy, recv494TzbhWJt9jC",recjKtGQI7YoomIxt,BunniesFromHell#722441,https://matcherino.com/tournaments/132276/admin/general,"recdz3yqlWnCbHyVA, rec75yK9G1rlEIkRW, recdYkJjqA1Uzqf9X, reciuq91Niz0jkSAJ, recc54jKc4I9TSq8w",BunniesFromHell,0,True,True,True,3,https://twitch.tv/matchstickmelee,https://www.start.gg/tournament/vortex-gallery-at-frosty-faustings-xvii/event/kamen-rider-super-climax-heroes/overview,https://matcherino.com/tournaments/132276,https://vortexgallery.moe/info#KRSCH,1,0,1,3,2,1,True,True,,0f81bc23,"recr3aTplUpT7qsZo, recZj8dOCmGgS8w5h, recxv85EF9ffbcHyk",2025-01-24T03:00:00.000Z,2025-01-24T16:00:00.000Z,3,3 Hours,BunniesFromHell,"@ComboFGC, @syndicatesnivy",Dolphin,"reczIQpQMZVTublU1, recDURQ6rernmFyHp",True,"None, MM",True,5,https://v5.airtableusercontent.com/v3