- No Items, No Final Smash Meter, No Stage Hazards","- Legal Stages:
  - STARTERS: Smashville, Small Battlefield,Battlefield, Pokemon Stadium 2,Town & City
  - COUNTERPICKS: Hollow Bastion, Kalos Pokemon Stadium, Final Destination

- Matches:
  - RPS for first ban, players ban 1-2-1 out of starter stages until one stage remains, then play on that stage
  - A double-blind may be requested before Game 1 begins when players select characters
  - After Game 1, the winner of Game 1 bans three stages of the eight legal stages, then the loser of Game 1 picks one of the remaining stages, then the winner of Game 1 chooses their character, then the loser of Game 1 chooses their character.
  - Repeat process until set ends

- Matches are First to Two Wins (Best Of 3)
- Matches for players in Top 8 are First to Three Wins (Best Of 5)
